Pomodoro Timer

Pomodoro Timer provides a convenient way, timer and notifications, to implement the Pomodoro Technique.

The Pomodoro Technique can be found here: http://pomodorotechnique.com/

USAGE:
Extract the files into ~/pomodorotimer
Run the command ./configure 
If you don't have a ~/bin directory that is in your PATH, instead place the executable file, or a symbolic link (better), in your PATH

To run the program use: pomodorotimer &
Then close the terminal.

Or use the application launcher, which should have been created.
